export default ()=>{
  return(

"pragma solidity ^0.4.26;" + "\n" + "\n" +

  "contract SampleContract{" + "\n" +
  "address public owner;" + "\n" +

  "uint public last_completed_migration;" + "\n" +  "\n" +

  "constructor() public {" + "\n" +
    "owner = msg.sender;" + "\n" +
  "}" + "\n" + "\n" +

  "modifier restricted() {" + "\n" +
    "if (msg.sender == owner) _;" + "\n" +
  "}" + "\n" +  "\n" +

  "function setCompleted(uint completed) public restricted {" + "\n" +
    "last_completed_migration = completed;" + "\n" +
  "}" + "\n" + "}" 



)
}
